<div class="one-third column">
  <div class="shimmed">
    <h3>Cone Patrol?</h3>
    <p>I heart skiing.  I double heart skiing powder.  "Cone Patrol" is a term a ski buddy gave to hiking the cone at <a href="http://mtbachelor.com">Mt. Bachelor</a> prior to opening for freshiez.</p><p>Born from that tradition is <em>conepatrol.com</em>, a way for you &ndash; the fellow shredder, to get powder alerts sent to your phone via text.</p>
    <p>So ditch the snow phone, and setup a <em>conepatrol</em> alert to shout at you when the goods have dropped.  See you on the cone!</p>
    <p>&ndash; @conepatrolapp</p>
  </div>
</div>
  <div class="one-third column">
    <div class="shimmed">
    <h3>How it Works</h3>
    <ul class="square">
      <li><p><strong>Ullr Delivers</strong>: Someday (soon) it will snow once again up at Mt. Bachelor.  As you slumber, lord Ullr will take a massive dump on our beloved hill, and we will all be stoked!</p></li>
      <li><p><strong><em>conepatrol</em> Texts</strong>: The trusty Cone Patrol robot scours the interwebs for the latest freshiez measurements.  Unlike your ski bro partner, the cp robot doesn't hook up with your girlfriend and then pass out and forget to look at conditions.</p></li>
      <li><p><strong>Make Turns</strong>: If there is enough freshies to suit your fancy, we send you a text.  You gear up, get stoked, and git sum.  No need to call the snow phone, or view a web page, you get notified when the gnar has arrived.</p></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="one-third column">
    <div class="highlight shimmed">
      <% if !shredder_signed_in? -%>
    <h3>Sign Up!</h3>
    <p>Signing up is super simple, and free!  Fill out this form, and we'll send you a confirmation text.  Its as easy as snowboarding!</p>
    <p>Enter your mobile number (10 digits no dashes/spaces), and select the new snow threshold to trigger an alert.</p>
    <%= form_for @shredder do |f| %>
      <%= f.label :email %>
      <%= f.text_field :email %>
      <%= f.label :password %>
      <%= f.password_field :password %>
      <%= f.label :password_confirmation %>
      <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation %>
      <%= f.label :mobile, 'Mobile:' %>
      <%= f.text_field :mobile %>
      <%= f.label :mobile, 'Freshies Threshold:' %>
      <%= f.select :inches, (2..12).collect{|i| ["#{i} or more inches",i]}, {:include_blank => false} %>
      <%= f.hidden_field :area_id, {:value => 1} %>
      <%= f.submit 'Sign Up', {:id=>'sign_up'} %>
    <% end %>
  <% else -%>
    <h3>Yo Buddy!!</h3>
    <% if current_shredder.confirmed? -%>

    <% else -%>
    <p>We need to confirm your mobile number before we can send alerts.  Click the button below to confirm you number (<%= current_shredder.mobile %>):</p>
    <a href="/confirm" class="button">Confirm Now</a>
    <% end -%>
  <% end -%>
  </div>
  </div>
